  <name>A smart custom ScrollView for Android</name>
  <description>A smart custom ScrollView for Android, which is able to measure your inside content length and decide whether a rightside vertical text-indicator or graphic-indicator is in need or not. With this smart container, compared with default Android ScrollView, users are given a more visualised notice that more content is hidden under the visible layout and the entire content can be viewed by scrolling.</description>
